{"tid":2357386,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社交網頁編輯指黃之鋒未有律師陪同下完成錄取口供程序","createTime":"2021-01-07T11:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T13:06:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a73231f3b53febf5674757644d5a140ee0a4d640","tid":2357386,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569176-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569176-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zyT1kznsNOvA2%2BdQC7BC3ts%3D&h=0bcc92c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569176-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8a401147\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569176-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n正在服刑的前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒，他的社交網頁編輯表示，黃之鋒親友接獲懲教署福利官通知，指黃之鋒因涉嫌違反國安法，今早由石壁監獄轉至荔枝角懲教所錄取口供，但<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">律師到場後未能會見黃之鋒，他沒有律師在陪同下完成錄取口供程序</span></span></strong>，並送返石壁監獄。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日拘捕53人，包括發起或參與去年民主派初選的人士，指他們涉嫌顛覆國家政權，警方說，其中6人是組織及策劃角色，其餘47人是參與者。"},{"pid":"401e86b98f21646b59b2b1818a2bdab05c7eda78","tid":2357386,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:41:09.000Z","msg":"好快就官派律師"},{"pid":"82f33c4930122381b763d50061e1083913331327","tid":2357386,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:44:21.000Z","msg":"應該都係我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a39b665b8ae8e502a0a6bbd94ec7b632c68503","tid":2357386,"uid":238475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:47:31.000Z","msg":"你估係未食晏之前就拉，等個人肚空空去審? 折磨人的手法有好多，睇路...."},{"pid":"61a23dbb2eace0ac2b80516df832e91159e6b171","tid":2357386,"uid":57675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"82f33c4930122381b763d5